: Be kind to neighbors, regardless of religion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 27, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Mujahid reported: We were with Abdullah ibn Amr while his servant prepared to distribute a sheep. Abdullah said, \u201cYoung man, when you are finished, then begin with our Jewish neighbor.\u201d A man said, \u201cJewish? May Allah correct you!\u201d Abdullah said, \u201cI heard the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37278,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/10\/31\/safeguarding-oaths-phrases\/","url_meta":{"origin":34135,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Shirk: Safeguarding words from lesser idolatry","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 31, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Qutaylah reported: A Jewish man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cIndeed, you are setting up rivals with Allah and associating partners with Him when you say, \u2018What Allah wills and you will,\u2019 and when you swear by the Ka\u2019bah!\u201d Then the Prophet\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20516,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/03\/31\/magic-spells-amulets-shirk\/","url_meta":{"origin":34135,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Spells: Amulets and charms are forbidden medicine","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, magic spells, amulets, and charms are acts of idolatry.\u201d Abdullah\u2019s wife, Zaynab, said, \u201cWhy do you say this? By Allah, I would go to a Jewish man when my eye was discharging. He would invoke a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37570,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/19\/salah-3-times\/","url_meta":{"origin":34135,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Salat: The Prophet stresses the greatness of prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 19, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: A man came to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and he asked him about the best of deeds. The Prophet said, \u201cPrayer.\u201d The man said, \u201cThen what?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen prayer.\u201d The man said, \u201cThen what?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThen\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33226,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/18\/allah-loves-family-ties\/","url_meta":{"origin":34135,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Rahim: Allah loves family ties, hates separation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 18, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Qatadah reported: A man of Khath\u2019am came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, asaying, \u201cAre you the one who considers himself the Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cYes.\u2